Uber driver Emerson Decarvalho allegedly ran down a cyclist after ramming into a cyclist who was shouting at him , leaving the biker with several broken bones , police say .
The incident occurred in the busy Fisherman 's Wharf area of San Francisco when the cyclist rode up to the vehicle , yelled at the driver , banged on his window .
The driver sustained a punctured lung , broken ribs and a broken clavicle .
Uber to in the incident .